name: RadicalNachoSmackdown
description:
Almost every key on your keyboard starts a new nacho ship player. Hold down your key to rotate and release to shoot. Tapping your key will propel your nacho forward. A scoreboard on the side says which key is doing best.

Crowd around your keyboard and see how many players you can get to compete!

Music is by PMSFX.

https://www.pmsfx.com/free
